            "id": 5908480,
            "title": "主攻股必備要件、波若威、華經、雙鴻、ITH、啟碁、力成",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>歷史總是不斷地重演</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股由空翻多三部曲：落底→築底→攻擊</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>目前就待最後一波衝擊波的出爐</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>多方準備拿回發球權</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>選股才是重點</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主攻股必備哪三大要件：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(1) 主攻股必會領先趨勢作上漲</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(2) 主攻股必會配合線型的要求</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(3) 主攻股必會符合行情的意義</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>譬如：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>矽光子概念股波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>同樣事矽光子上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>) 股價高檔震盪拉回</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>但是，為何波若威能夠一路噴出大漲上來？</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要是受惠 AI 大廠輝達黃仁勳 CPO 加持點名</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>將打破過去超大規模以及企業網路面臨的限制</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>隨著矽光子技術往前邁進一步，將為相關供應鏈帶來巨大的成長動能</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>符合低基期、具轉機成長概念題材</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>這樣各位懂得吧！</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>資訊軟體華經 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2468:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2468\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2468-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>為何股價能夠連二日噴漲停再創新高？</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>因為受惠 Google 母公司 Alphabet 發動其歷來最大併購案</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>收購雲端資安公司 Wiz，打造更強大的雲端生態系</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>帶動相關資安概念股華經、驊宏資 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6148:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6148\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6148-TW</a>) 等個股的大漲</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其它包括：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>散熱一哥雙鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>)：GB300 推出將全面採用水冷散熱商機，帶動營收及獲利持續往前衝</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>小聯發科 ITH-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6962:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6962\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6962-TW</a>)：OLED 滲透率攀升，智慧型手機、筆電及車載等各產品線全面成長</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>網通大廠啟碁 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6285:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6285\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6285-TW</a>)：低軌衛星、智能駕駛規格及 WiFi 7 規格升級，帶動營運看俏</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>記憶體封測力成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6239:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6239\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6239-TW</a>)：美光大舉下單、日本鎧俠及陸系客戶追單，營運將自 Q2 轉強</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>機器人概念股佳能 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2374:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2374\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2374-TW</a>)：車載感測模組、邊緣 AI 及機器視覺模組等產品線帶動營運轉機大成長</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>逢低也都值得留意</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>甚至護國神山台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 及 AI 伺服器龍頭鴻海(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>隨著本益比修正、估值已回到合理投資價值區間，也都具備反彈的契機</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>操作其實可以不一樣</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>我喜歡買在股價小時候</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>我堅持操作主流人氣股</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>我喜歡大波段操作賺大錢</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>各位只要把握住一個原則</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>估值偏高的漲高股、不要碰、不要搶！</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>選擇低基期、具轉機成長題材的好股票</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>就會是贏家</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>別讓恐慌阻礙您的財富成長</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>【廣宇第二】下週集結進場</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>想要跟上的好朋友</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大師兄親自手把手帶你來佈局</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>歡迎大家一起共襄盛舉</p></se